{"tid":2283143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高永文：警告疫情會再爆 美制疫苗成效存疑 冀不涉政治影響","createTime":"2020-11-12T10:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T17:19:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca00342f52c0af431b489aaf94df991a4cde39e","tid":2283143,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"高永文呼籲市民要有心理準備繼續面對疫情<br />\n<br />\n食物及衛生局前局長高永文表示，對近來疫情走勢反覆非常擔心，呼籲市民要支持及配合政府防疫措施，亦要有心理準備病毒不會在短時間內離開本港。他認為現階段的防疫措施足夠，相信政府在有需要時會再加強，又認為本港的感染控制追蹤工作已做得足夠。<br />\n<br />\n對於輝瑞藥廠宣布，測試中的新型冠狀病毒疫苗有效程度超過9成，高永文認為要等正式的科學文獻，才能確定疫苗的有效性，認為市民不能對疫苗開發過份樂觀，他希望疫苗的開發，分配不會被經濟及政治因素影響，並期望可以透過世衛協調機制解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2365974&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Bymt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=94609d89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365974</a>"},{"pid":"3d221abaa3fd9a11940e4065cfcb88593b77dbaa","tid":2283143,"uid":335434,"like":210,"dislike":1,"score":209,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"如果當年沙士可以用高水文畜生換返謝婉雯醫生返嚟你話幾好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4a027b4c2f0c968c06946f03f3b0d6348293aa","tid":2283143,"uid":3149,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"唔信輝瑞唔通信你啲支那貨咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9661670f4de961f3863c190116475c458b57a2","tid":2283143,"uid":37528,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩，鳩永文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d981bc054426c2a308b347b2f18d727ebae03bd","tid":2283143,"uid":270308,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-1